description: Telex is a humanist sans serif conceived to be a web font with nice legibility at normal text sizes. Originally based on grid fitting shapes it became a multi-purpose typeface with low contrast, open counter forms, wide proportions and a touch of freshness. Designed by Andrés Torresi for Huerta Tipográfica.
